<div id="about-me" class="about">
  <h1>ABOUT ME</h1>
  <hr style="width:40%">
  <div class="aboutme-grid">
    <div class="presentation">
      <%= image_tag "profile.JPG", class: 'Profile pic' %>
      <p>I'm a <strong>Full Stack Web Developer</strong> with a background in the teaching industry.
        I believe we can make a <strong>positive impact</strong> in the society with code, be it to your local community or in a bigger scale.
        <br>
        <br>
        I also have interest in Data Science and Applied Machine Learning to solve Real-World problems, so... please don't get too confused if you see some ML / AI project mixed in!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="tech-stack">
      <h2>MY TECH STACK</h2>
      <hr style="width:20%">
      <div class="stack">
        <div class="front-back-others">
          <h3>Front End</h3>
          <div class="icons-grid">
            <div class="icon">
              <p id='js'>JS ES6</p>
              <%= image_tag 'javascript.png' %>
